Episodes.Title: Episode 1
Episodes.Plot: When a devastating bomb explodes in central London, causing multiple deaths, a terrorist group with a hatred for human life claim responsibility. With their leader facing extradition, the bombers announce that crippling attacks will be launched at ten hour intervals until he is released.

Episodes.Title: Episode 2
Episodes.Plot: Zafar and Adam race against the clock to uncover the latest bomb. As a new ultimatum is issued and Tash mysteriously disapears, the team is forced to deal with the possibility of a mole within their own organisation.

Episodes.Title: Episode 3
Episodes.Plot: Far-right political party The British Way is threatening democracy so Adam and Fiona go undercover to infiltrate and destroy its campaign.
Episodes.GuestStars: Rupert Graves, Joanna Burnett, Dicker James, David Threlfall, Mark Flitton, Steven Pacey, Margot Leicester

Episodes.Title: Episode 4
Episodes.Plot: Adam infiltrates a truck carrying illegal immigrants across Europe in order to stop a would-be terrorist.
Episodes.GuestStars: Lewis Alsamari, Silas Carson, Goran Kostic, Chris Walker, Sarah Matravers, Charles Daish

Episodes.Title: Episode 5
Episodes.Plot: A neo-conservative group murder an ex-minister to cover up his past and then they hunt down the journalist who is threatening to blow the story and is under MI5 protection.
Episodes.GuestStars: Stanley Townsend, Simon Lenagan, Debra Gillett, Andrew Burt, Douglas Hodge

Episodes.Title: Episode 6
Episodes.Plot: MI5 suspect a terrorist is planning an attack from his prison cell.  Guest stars Jimi Mistry.
Episodes.GuestStars: Ralph Brown, Jimi Mistry, Joey Ansah, Alki David, Debra Gillett, Joanna Roth

Episodes.Title: Episode 7
Episodes.Plot: The Syrian foreign minister tries to establish subversive contacts with MI5 at the opening of a cultural centre in London. Fiona is desperate to lead this mission and must confront her Syrian past.
Episodes.GuestStars: Nathalie Armin, Darrell D'Silva, Sam Dastor, Khalid Laith

Episodes.Title: Episode 8
Episodes.Plot: An old British traitor is called on to infiltrate a Russian firm suspected of stealing secrets from GCHQ.

Episodes.Title: Episode 9
Episodes.Plot: Harry upsets the CIA by stopping an extradition to the USA.

Episodes.Title: Episode 10
Episodes.Plot: A former officer is convinced that MI5 killed Princess Diana and is determined to force the team to prove it.
